Place Name: Mine Creek Civil War Battlefield State Historic Site
Description: The museum did have some interesting artifacts, information and beautiful trails.  We were also warned about ticks.  Make sure that you spray yourself before you go on the trails.

Place Name: Battle Of Island Mound State Historic Site
Description: Easy stop, quick visit, but a cool piece of history. The trail was well maintained and the bathroom was also well maintained.  Check out my instagram post on this site: @mikeisoutside

Place Name: Mine Creek Battlefield Interpretive Walking Trail

Description: A very well put together and maintained museum depicting the civil war. The walking trails through the battlefield are well kept and easy to maneuver
